    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DodgeKill is not your typical game. Here, there's no character to control—your cursor is the one taking all the action! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Minimalist yet dynamic </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A game visually simple, some geometric shapes, a few colors, and that's all. <br>But if we combine all this, we get a game with varied enemies and complex challenges! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Easy to learn, hard to master </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Is it playable with only the mouse ? Absolutely!  <br>You just need to move the cursor. But make no mistake, even if the controls are simple, the game remains no less complicated!  <br>(Controllers and touchscreens are also compatible 🙂) </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A unique gameplay playable entirely with the mouse </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various level filled with surprises, for increasingly difficult challenges </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A tough difficulty that tests your nerves and will give you great satisfaction with each victory </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple and intuitive controls, accessible to all players </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenges available to increase the difficulty even more </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ready to take on the challenge ? </strong></p>",
